					<div class="rounded-2xl p-5 my-4 border border-gray-200" style="background-color: white;">
						<h4 class="font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;">Drill 1: The Name Drill</h4>
						<p>Type your name. Sound it out in Tibetan and try to spell it. <span class="tibetan-text">ཇོན་</span> (John)? <span class="tibetan-text">མེར་ཡི་</span> (Mary)? This makes it personal.</p>
