					<div class="rounded-2xl p-5 my-4 border border-gray-200" style="background-color: white;">
						<h4 class="font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Merriweather', serif;">Drill 2: The 5-Word Daily</h4>
						<p>Every day, type 5 vocabulary words you know. <span class="tibetan-text">མི</span> (person), <span class="tibetan-text">ཆུ</span> (water), <span class="tibetan-text">ཁ་པར</span> (phone). Muscle memory builds here.</p>
